      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i walk into the kitchen and i still expect to hear him making coffee or just humming some song... but there's nothing. it's just this heavy, empty silence that follows me from room to room. i don't even know why i'm bothering to get out of bed anymore. what's the point of just existing in a house that feels like a tomb?",
